How to translate the game with Rei Patcher
By Pokums
Currently, the game does not support English language and probably not going to be translated due to involvement of Chinese word games. This is a guide on how to install an auto translation patch to translate it to English or any other desired language that is supported by Google Translate.

How to install
  1. Follow this [github.com] link and download XUnity.AutoTranslator-ReiPatcher-[version number].zip of the latest release.
  2. After unpacking the archive place SetupReiPatcherAndAutoTranslator.exe into the game root folder (ex: \Steam\steamapps\common\Swaying Girl) .
  3. Run SetupReiPatcherAndAutoTranslator.exe and close command prompt after installation.
  4. Launch SwayingGirl (Patch and Run) to generate necessary folders and close the game.
  5. Go to newly created \Swaying Girl\AutoTranslator folder and open Config.ini with text editor.
  6. There change what comes after Language= to language you want to translate to (like en or ru) and what comes after FromLanguage= to zh-CN or auto .
  7. Save and quit the config file.
  8. Delete _AutoGeneratedTranslations.txt (previously auto-generated translations) from \Swaying Girl\AutoTranslator\Translation\en\Text .
  9. Now the game is patched, in-game text should automatically translate from Chinese (some texts take a little bit of time to be translated if they weren't seen before) and you can launch it directly from Steam.

Additional info
If you don't know your country's language code, you can look it up here. [sites.google.com]

Special thanks to bbepis [github.com] and github contributors for this patch!
